[img]https://file.garden/YB22oQJoG19Io7Up/jari%3Adota/00070.png[/img] 
 
 You shoot up with a nervous bolt, eyes adjusting to the new lighting. Instinctually, your hand goes to your blanket, but... 
 
You feel nothing. There isn't a blanket here, which you could SWEAR you had used to tuck yourself under the covers when you'd passed out at your... 
 
No, wait, you hadn't been in bed, you'd been at your desk, right? 
 
This isn't either of them. 
 
Instead, your hands find the plush polyester of a pleather (yet comfy) couch. The sag shifts under your hands, as if there is someone next to you. 
 
[spoiler]
[color=#008141]KANAYA: Are You Okay[/color] 
[color=#008141]KANAYA: Zara You Were Screaming[/color] 
[color=#e00707]ZARA: was i?[/color] 
[/spoiler]
Oh, right, of course, there was someone next to you. You suddenly have a lack of understanding of jack shit, and this situation makes perfect sense. 
 
[spoiler]
[color=#e00707]ZARA: wait[/color] 
[/spoiler]

[img]https://file.garden/YB22oQJoG19Io7Up/jari%3Adota/00071.gif[/img] 
 
 Ah, a minor correction. You have no fucking clue what the fuck is going on. 
 
[spoiler]
[color=#e00707]ZARA: WHAT THE FUCK[/color] 
[color=#e00707]ZARA: HOLY SHIT[/color] 
[color=#008141]KANAYA: Zara You Seem To Be Greatly Distressed[/color] 
[color=#008141]KANAYA: You Are Scaring Me[/color] 
[color=#e00707]ZARA: lady YOURE scaring ME[/color] 
[/spoiler]

[img]https://file.garden/YB22oQJoG19Io7Up/jari%3Adota/00072.png[/img] 
 
 Questions buzz in your brain; prominently, the ever-important "when the fuck did i agree to spend the night with a Little Monsters extra," warring with "who the fuck is she," the conflict boiling over into panic. The face of the bizarrely familiar alien who you have never seen before in your life fills with concern. 
 
[spoiler]
[color=#008141]KANAYA: What Is Going On[/color] 
[color=#008141]KANAYA: This Is Not Like You[/color] 
[color=#e00707]ZARA: and you know what is???[/color] 
[color=#008141]KANAYA: I At Least Know That I Have Never Heard You Shout Before[/color] 
[/spoiler]
She scoots over to you, her eyes filled with worry, brow furrowed. 
Your body reacts at the same time you do. 
 
[spoiler]
[color=#e00707]ZARA: get away from me[/color] 
[/spoiler]

p.c: A panic and a freakout later...
